{"tid":687832,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)明日之後 屍營旅舍 蒐屍魔2","createTime":"2018-06-02T15:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T19:05:57.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"abaf278200da953d37ccf3110f673c772a56fb8b","tid":687832,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:01:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=sMYxUHRkZZkXU%2BYeR80TAjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=790d962e\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=sMYxUHRkZZkXU%2BYeR80TAjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=ef32dbb7\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=sMYxUHRkZZkXU%2BYeR80TAjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=8209c02a\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/58/The_Day_After_Tomorrow_movie.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F58%2FThe_Day_After_Tomorrow_movie.jpg&h=bc58c67a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/1/10/The_Cabin_in_the_Woods.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F1%2F10%2FThe_Cabin_in_the_Woods.jpg&h=213436b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/e9/TheCollectionPoster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fe9%2FTheCollectionPoster.jpg&h=53085010&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.在一片已經極度融化的南極冰川上，古氣候學家傑克&middot;霍爾與同事弗蘭克和傑森在冰川上考察時，親眼目睹整個拉森冰架全部斷裂。傑克隨後將有關全球暖化調查結果，在新德里舉行的聯合國研討會上作出報告，聲明兩極冰川融化已經阻斷了北大西洋洋流的暖洋流，而這種情況繼續持續下去將會在未來形成另一個冰河時期。但參加會議的各國元首對此感到荒謬，美國副總統雷蒙&middot;貝克甚至把傑克的理論當作笑話看待。傑克回到華盛頓後致電自己的妻子露西，得知自己兒子山姆即將去紐約參加科學知識競賽<br />\n<br />\n2.故事講述五名青年男女去森林度假屋遊玩，可是卻遇上恐怖血腥事件，遊玩變成被虐殺，但其實這並不是一間普通房屋，房子的牆後還有一間耐人尋味的控制室，還有人在背後操控&hellip;&hellip;.<br />\n<br />\n3.蒐屍魔舉辦狂歡派對，邀請全城帥哥辣妹來共襄盛舉，艾莉娜與朋友們更是盛裝出席，而這些誤入陷阱的年青人，都成為他的完美收藏。<br />\n曾經從蒐屍魔魔掌中逃過一劫的阿金，因為嚴重精神創傷，在醫院接受長期的心理治療，卻突然遭人挾持綁架。教唆綁架阿金的人，正是艾莉娜的父親。他提出巨額的報酬，強迫阿金組成搜救隊，前往殺人魔家中進行探查，希望可以救回自己的女兒...<br />\n<br />\n11 25PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=sMYxUHRkZZkXU%2BYeR80TAjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=9cdcdb22\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=sMYxUHRkZZkXU%2BYeR80TAjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=2ae5a19f\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b64ee5a247d60a07b1637f4e4de5e8ff1bf42f","tid":687